spirit:component.spirit:description: Audio Clock Recovery Unit is used to recover the Audio clock from a given reference clock. This IP can be used with HDMI, DP and SDI to recover the Audio clock. This IP can also be used along with I2S Transmitter to recover the Audio clock to compensate the jitter and PPM variation in the reference clock.
